   (1) 💬 ## Summary
   (1) 💬 
   (1) 💬 Implemented the todo.md item **"Buffer padding + input region for shadows"** for promoted `<popover>` → `xdg_popup` surfaces:
   (1) 💬 
   (1) 💬 - Added `popover_content_padding()` / `shadow_filter_extended_bounds()` in `crates/core/shell/src/shell/component/shell_component.rs`, reusing the existing shadow/blur damage-extent math (previously only used for present-damage tracking) to compute how much a popover's buffer needs to grow beyond its content box.
