   (1) 💬 - The popup buffer, positioner size, and painted subtree now use the padded size/offset; the positioner's `offset` is compensated by `-content_offset` so anchored content doesn't visually shift; the Wayland input region is masked back down to the true content rect (mirroring the existing tooltip pattern), so clicks over the shadow padding pass through.
